<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="my">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TDI Game Shop Links</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #8A2BE2; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
            color: white;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 110px;
            height: 110px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid #00d2ff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .username {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .description {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            max-width: 320px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .link-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .link-card {
            background-color: #E066FF; 
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0px #000; 
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .link-card:hover {
            transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
            box-shadow: 7px 7px 0px #000;
            background-color: #f080ff;
        }

        .link-card:active {
            transform: translate(2px, 2px);
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 0px #000;
        }

        .icon {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .text {
            flex-grow: 1;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .dots {
            font-size: 20px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <img src="https://i.ibb.co/4wkzx3cM/image.jpg" alt="TDI Game Shop" class="profile-img">
    <div class="username">@TDI Game Shop</div>
    <p class="description">
        TDI Game Shop မှာ Game Items များစွာကို <br>
        ယုံကြည်စိတ်ချစွာ ဝယ်ယူနိုင်ပါပြီ။
    </p>

    <div class="link-container">

        <a href="http://tdi.alphacloud.store" target="_blank" class="link-card">
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1006/1006771.png" class="icon" alt="Website">
            <span class="text">Game Shop Website ဒေါင်းရန်နှိပ်ပါ</span>
            <span class="dots"></span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://t.me/TDI_Game_Shop_Bot" target="_blank" class="link-card">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/82/Telegram_logo.svg" class="icon" alt="Telegram Bot">
            <span class="text">Telegram Bot သို့ ဆက်သွယ်ရန်</span>
            <span class="dots"></span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://t.me/TDIGameShop40" target="_blank" class="link-card">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/82/Telegram_logo.svg" class="icon" alt="Telegram Channel">
            <span class="text">Telegram Channel</span>
            <span class="dots"></span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://t.me/TDIGameShop4" target="_blank" class="link-card">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/82/Telegram_logo.svg" class="icon" alt="Owner Account">
            <span class="text">Owner Account</span>
            <span class="dots"></span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/19wq2K9ErS/" target="_blank" class="link-card">
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5968/5968764.png" class="icon" alt="Facebook">
            <span class="text">Facebook Page</span>
            <span class="dots"></span>
        </a>

    </div>

</body>
</html>

